#####################
Fuse-7z: Installation
#####################

Requirements
############

You need the following libraries:

- libfuse >= 2.8
  http://fuse.sourceforge.net
- lib7zip >= 0.8
  http://www.nih.at/libzip/

The following tools are required:

- C++ compiler
  g++ 4.2.3 or other modern C++ compiler
- pkg-config
  http://pkg-config.freedesktop.org/
- waf
  https://code.google.com/p/waf/

Build Instructions
##################

To build fuse-7z do the following:

- get the waf build system that is used to build fuse-7z::

    $ wget https://waf.googlecode.com/files/waf-1.7.11 -O waf

- configure::

    $ python waf configure --prefix=/usr

- build::

    $ python waf

- install::

    $ python waf install --destdir=/

